<div id="cookieconsent" style="position: fixed; bottom: 0px; width: 100%; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); display: none; z-index: 9999999;">
<div class="content" style="max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding-top: 1.4rem; padding-bottom: 1.4rem; overflow-y: hidden;">
<div class="text" style="color: #fff; display: inline-block; width: 67%; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 1.5rem;"><strong>We use cookies</strong> to provide you with the best experience across all Scoop News Group websites. By using Scoop News Group websites, you consent to the use of cookies. <a href="https://scoopnewsgroup.com/privacy" target="_blank" style="color: #8733ff; text-decoration: none; font-style: italic; font-weight: 500;">Learn more</a></div>
<div class="cookiebtn" style="display: inline-block; width: 25%; vertical-align: middle;"><button id="gotit" class="gotit" style="margin-left: 2rem; color: #fff; background-color: #8733ff; font-family:'Oswald',sans-serif; font-weight: bold; border: none; width: 10rem; padding-bottom: 1.4rem; padding-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.6rem;">GOT IT!</button></div>
